Margaret Ehrlich https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Ehrlich 0 Margaret Ehrlich (1917 – January 12, 1936) was a dancer and motion picture actress from Milwaukee, Wisconsin. Her career in Hollywood was cut short by an auto accident. Her true surname was Earlich. She was a graduate of Santa Monica High School.
